parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the timing chain can cause the engine to seize or lock up, leading to a loss of power and control, which can result in accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The engine makes a loud noise
the vehicle stalls or loses power
the "Drive Train Malfunction" warning light appears
and the vehicle may enter limp mode.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the VANOS solenoid bolts can cause the engine to malfunction, leading to a loss of power and control, which can result in accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The engine makes a loud noise
the "Drive Train Malfunction" warning light appears
and the vehicle may enter limp mode.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the fuel pump can cause the engine to stall or lose power, leading to a loss of control, which can result in accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The engine stalls or loses power
the "Low Oil Pressure" warning light appears
and the vehicle may enter limp mode.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the valve cover gasket can cause oil leaks, leading to engine damage and potentially causing a fire.
symptoms: White smoke appears from the hood and air vents
the engine makes a loud noise
and the "Check Engine" warning light appears.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Engine oil leaks can cause engine damage and potentially lead to a fire.
symptoms: Oil leaks from the engine
the "Check Engine" warning light appears
and the engine makes a loud noise.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the passenger occupancy sensor can cause the passenger airbag system to malfunction, leading to potential injury or death in the event of a collision.
symptoms: The passenger airbag warning light is illuminated
the passenger airbag system is disabled
the passenger seat belt warning is displayed
the airbag system malfunctions intermittently
and the passenger airbag fails to deploy in the event of a collision.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Takata Airbag Recall Parts Distribution Disconnect
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unavailability of recall parts for the Takata airbag recall can cause a delay in the repair, leaving the vehicle in an unsafe condition and potentially leading to injury or death in the event of a collision.
symptoms: The recall notice is received
but the parts are unavailable
the dealer is unable to perform the repair
and the manufacturer is unable to provide an estimated time for parts availability.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the timing chain can cause the engine to shut down, leading to a loss of power and control, which can result in accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The engine shuts down
the vehicle loses power
the "Drivetrain Malfunction" error message appears
the vehicle stalls
and the engine makes unusual noises.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the oil pump can cause the engine to shut down, leading to a loss of power and control, which can result in accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The engine shuts down
the vehicle loses power
the "Low Oil Pressure" warning message appears
the engine makes unusual noises
and the vehicle stalls.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The drivetrain malfunction can cause the vehicle to lose power, leading to a loss of control, which can result in accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The "Drivetrain Malfunction" error message appears
the vehicle loses power
the engine shuts down
and the vehicle stalls.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the fuel system can cause the vehicle to lose power, leading to a loss of control, which can result in accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle loses power
the engine shuts down
the "Low Fuel" warning message appears
and the vehicle stalls.
